'''山蟛蜞菊'''（[[学名|学名]]：{{lang|la|''Wollastonia montana''}}）是[[菊科|菊科]][[孿花菊屬|孿花菊屬]]的植物。

== 分布 ==
本種分布于[[台灣|台灣]]<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Wollastonia montana (Blume) DC. (Asteraceae), a newly recorded plant in Taiwan|author=Shih-Wen Chung, Tian-Chuan Hsu|url=https://www.tesri.gov.tw/A15_2/download1/31225/6|journal=''Taiwan Journal of Biodiversity''|issue=16|doi=|others=|year=2014|volume=4|page=399- 404|pmid=}}</ref>、[[越南|越南]]、[[尼泊爾|尼泊爾]]、[[緬甸|緬甸]]、[[泰國|泰國]]、[[爪哇|爪哇]]，以及[[中国|中国]]的南部和西南部各省区，生长于海拔500米至800米的地区，多生在路旁、溪边或山区沟谷中<ref>{{cite web|title=山蟛蜞菊|url=http://www.bioinfo.cn/db05/KmzwSpecies.php?action=view&id=5263|accessdate=2009-02-25|author=昆明植物研究所|work=《中国高等植物数据库全库》|publisher=中国科学院微生物研究所|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305101459/http://www.bioinfo.cn/db05/KmzwSpecies.php?action=view&id=5263|archivedate=2016-03-05|deadurl=yes}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Indocypraea montana (Blume) Orchard {{!}} Plants of the World Online {{!}} Kew Science|url=http://powo.science.kew.org/taxon/urn:lsid:ipni.org:names:77136425-1|accessdate=2020-09-23|work=Plants of the World Online|language=en|archive-date=2022-04-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220417140848/https://powo.science.kew.org/taxon/urn:lsid:ipni.org:names:77136425-1}}</ref>。

== 分類學 ==
有學者將本種獨立為[[山蟛蜞菊屬|山蟛蜞菊屬]]（''Indocypraea''）<ref>{{Cite journal|title=The Wollastonia/Melanthera/Wedelia generic complex (Asteraceae: Ecliptinae), with particular reference to Australia and Malesia|author=Anthony E. Orchard|url=https://florabase.dpaw.wa.gov.au/nuytsia/article/659|journal=''Nuytsia''|issue=23|doi=|others=|year=2013|volume=|page=337–466|pmid=|access-date=2020-09-23|archive-date=2020-07-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200718143934/https://florabase.dpaw.wa.gov.au/nuytsia/article/659|dead-url=no}}</ref>，但其單系性仍有待後續驗證，有研究認為其仍屬於孿花菊屬的一員<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Biogeography and relationships within the Melanthera alliance: A pan-tropical lineage (Compositae: Heliantheae: Ecliptinae)|author=|url=http://doi.wiley.com/10.12705/673.6|last=Edwards|first=Robert D.|last2=Cantley|first2=Jason T.|date=2018-06-01|journal=''Taxon''|issue=3|doi=10.12705/673.6|others=|year=|volume=67|page=|pages=552–564|language=en|issn=0040-0262|pmid=|last3=Chau|first3=Marian M.|last4=Keeley|first4=Sterling C.|last5=Funk|first5=Vicki A.}}</ref>。

